text: Colobothea aleata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1885. It is known from Mexico and Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Colobothea aleata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1885
title: Colobothea aleata
